#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have used a burning program such as Nero under Windows, &k3b; will "
"feel quite familiar."
msgstr ""
"Ako ste koristili programe za prženje kao što je Nero u Windowsu, &k3b; će "
"djelovati jako poznato."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Featuring a simple, yet powerful graphical interface, &k3b; provides various "
"options for burning a CD, DVD, or BD (Blu-ray disc). Various types of "
"optical projects are supported including (but not limited to) audio and "
"data, video projects for DVD and VCD, as well as multi-session and mixed-"
"mode discs. &k3b; also has the ability to erase re-writeable media and can "
"perform more complicated tasks such as audiovisual encoding and decoding."
msgstr ""
"Jednostavan, ali moćan grafički interfejs, &k3b; obezbjeđuje različite "
"opcije za prženje CDova, DVDova, ili BDova ( Blu-ray disc). Podržani su "
"različiti tipovi optičkih projekata uključujući audio i podatkovne projekte, "
"video projekte za DVD i VCD, kao i više-sesijske i više-načinske diskove. "
"&k3b; takođe ima mogućnost da obriše ponovo upisive medije i može izvesti "
"još komplikovanije zadatke kao što su audiovizualno kodiranje i dekodiranje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pre-setup"
msgstr "Pred-postavke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you run &k3b; for the first time, you may find &k3b; informing you that "
"no optical writer drivers have been found, meaning you will not be able to "
"write to any optical discs. There is no need to panic as &k3b; will open the "
"<guilabel>Permissions</guilabel> tab on the <guilabel>Programs</guilabel> "
"page of the configuration dialog, where permissions can now be changed. In "
"all modern systems optical devices belongs to a certain user group (&eg; "
"<quote>cdrom</quote>). If the current user does not belongs to this group, "
"he is offered to add himself to it on this tab."
msgstr ""
"Kada pokrenete &k3b; po prvi put, &k3b; vas može informisati da nisu nađeni "
"drajevri optičkog pisača, što znači da nećete biti u mogućnosti da pišete na "
"nekom od optičkih diskova. Nema potrebe za paniku jer će &k3b; otvoriti tab "
"<guilabel>Dopuštenja</guilabel> na strani <guilabel>Programs</guilabel> "
"konfiguracijskog dijaloga, gdje sada dopuštenja mogu biti promijenjena. U "
"svim modernim sistemima optički uređaji pripadaju određenoj korisničkoj "
"grupi (&eg; <quote>cdrom</quote>). Ako trenutni korisnik ne pripada ovoj "
"grupi, ponuđeno mu je da doda sam sebe u ovaj tab."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring the User Interface"
msgstr "Konfigurisanje Korisničkog interfesja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Upon starting &k3b; you are offered quick starts to the three most popular "
"processes"
msgstr ""
"Pri startanju &k3b;-a ponuđeni su vam brzi startovi tri najpopularnija "
"procesa"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "New Data Project"
msgstr "Novi podatkovni projekat"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "New Audio CD Project"
msgstr "Novi Audio CD projekt"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy Medium"
msgstr "Medijum kopiranja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&k3b; can perform much more than these tasks though, and so you may find "
"that some of the other possibilities are just as useful to you. Take a look "
"at this list for a taste of other available functions:"
msgstr ""
"&k3b; može izvršiti mnogo više ovih zadataka, tako da možete vidjeti da su "
"druge mogućnosti isto tako korisne za vas. Pogledajte listu drugih "
"dozvoljenih funkcija:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Perhaps a quick start for one or more of these other tasks would be useful "
"to you and so &k3b; can give you that, too. Simply right click on the "
"application desktop, and here you will see a menu for adding buttons:"
msgstr ""
"Možda brzi start jednog od više od ovih zadataka može biti korisno za vas, "
"pa vam &k3b;  može i to omogućiti. Jednostavno kliknite desnim klik na "
"desktop aplikacije, i ovdje ćete vidjeti meni za dodavanje dugmadi:"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring the internals"
msgstr "Unutrašnja konfiguracija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Most of the default settings can simply be left alone. It is however, "
"recommended that you do take a look at the <guilabel>Advanced Settings</"
"guilabel> page. Here you can set various important settings, if required."
msgstr ""
"Većina zadanih postavki mogu jednostavno biti ostavljene same. Međutim, "
"preporučeno je da pogledate <guilabel>Napredne postavke</guilabel> stranicu. "
"Ovdje možete postaviti mnogo važnih postavki, ako je porebno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Use Burnfree</guilabel> should be set - it controls the burn, "
"ensuring that the buffer never gets dangerously low (which reduces the "
"quantity of bad burns)."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Koristi slobodno prženje</guilabel> trebao bi biti setovan - "
"kontroliše prženje, osiguravajući da bafer nikada ne postane opasno (što "
"smanjuje količinu loših prženja)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid "You may wish to automatically erase re-writable disks."
msgstr "Možete željeti da automatski zbrišete ponovo upisive diskove."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The option <guilabel>Do not eject medium after write process</guilabel> is "
"invaluable if your drive is one that cannot be closed quickly enough for "
"<guilabel>Verify</guilabel> to happen."
msgstr ""
"Opcija <guilabel>Ne vaditi medijum nakon procesa pisanja</guilabel> je "
"neprocjenjiv ako vaš uređaj ne može biti zatvoren dovoljno brzo da bi se  "
"<guilabel>Potvrdi</guilabel> akcija desila."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preparing to burn a disk"
msgstr "Priprema za prženje diska"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When starting a new project, you should ensure that &k3b; has detected the "
"correct optical media, such as CD or DVD. On the status line at the bottom "
"of the screen you should see the size of disk which is currently set. If "
"this is not correct, or you require a different size, simply right-click on "
"it and set the preferred size from the provided list:"
msgstr ""
"Kada započnete novi projekat, trebali biste osigurati da je &k3b; detektovao "
"tačan optički medij, kao šsto je CD ili DVD. Na statusnoj liniji na dnu "
"ekrana trebali biste vidjeti veličinu diska koji je trenutno postavljen. Ako "
"ovo nije tačno, ili tražite drugačiju veličinu, jednostavno kliknite lijevim "
"klikom na to i postavite željenu veličinu iz obezbjeđene liste:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid "Now choose what is to be burnt."
msgstr "Sada odaberite šta treba biti prženo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:172
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The top half of the screen is the <emphasis>source pane</emphasis>; it "
"functions like a file manager. You can choose ordinary files from mounted "
"data volumes or audio tracks from inserted audio discs. Names of audio "
"tracks are automatically read from CD-Text data, if your CD drive supports "
"reading it, or generated using <ulink url=\"http://libcddb.sourceforge.net/"
"\">CDDB</ulink>; the exact format is controlled by a button in the bottom "
"pane. If the names are incorrect or simply do not match the description of "
"the disc, you can edit them using the toolbar button. Your changes will be "
"cached locally and submitted to the master registry at <ulink url=\"http://"
"www.freedb.org/\">FreeDB</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Gornja polovina ekrana je <emphasis>izvorni okvir</emphasis>; on funkcioniše "
"kao menadžer datoteka. Možete odabrati obične datoteke iz montirane količine "
"podataka ili audio numera iz umetnutih audio diskova. Imena audio numera su "
"automatski pročitane iz CD-TEXT podataka, ako vaš CD pogon podržava čitanje, "
"ili je generisan korištenjem <ulink url=\"http://libcddb.sourceforge.net/"
"\">CDDB</ulink>; tačan format je kontrolisan dugmetom u donjem okviru. Ako "
"su imena netačna ili jednostavno ne odgovaraju opisu diska, možete ih "
"editovati koristeći dugme alatnu traku. Vaše promjene će biti lokalno "
"memorirana i podnešena glavnom registru na <ulink url=\"http://www.freedb."
"org/\">FreeDB</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the whole record is performed by the same artist, leave the track artist "
"entries blank, fill the <guilabel>Album artist</guilabel>, save to CDDB and "
"requery."
msgstr ""
"Ako je cijeli snimak izveden od strane istog izvođača, ostavite prazna polja "
"za unos izvođača, ispunite <guilabel>Izvođač abuma</guilabel>, spremite u "
"CDDB i osvježite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now that you have your sources at hand, simply drag and drop the files and "
"directories you wish to burn onto the large pane to the right at the bottom; "
"this is the <emphasis>model pane</emphasis>. Behold a tree of your chosen "
"files forming to the left. Should there be some files or directories which "
"you do not want to burn, these can be easily removed from the project by "
"simply removing them from the panel at the bottom. Select the file to be "
"removed (you can control-click to select multiple ones), then choose "
"<guilabel>Remove</guilabel> from the context menu."
msgstr ""
"Sada kada imate vaše izvore pri ruci, jednostavno povucite i ispistute "
"datoteke i direktorije koje želite pržiti na veliki okvir desno na dnu; ovo "
"je <emphasis>model okvir</emphasis>. Posmatrajte stablo koje vaše datoteke "
"formiraju lijevo. Ako tamo postoje datoteke i direktorije koje ne želite "
"pržiti, one mogu biti lako uklonjene iz projekta jednostavno ih uklanjajući "
"iz panela na dnu. Odaberite datoteku koja treba biti uklonjena (kontrola-"
"klikom možete selektovati više stavki), onda odaberite then choose "
"<guilabel>Ukloni</guilabel> iz kontekstnog menija."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you need to compress audio, create a new audio CD project, add the files "
"to be converted and press the button <guilabel>Convert Tracks</guilabel>. "
"This will not affect the contents of the CD if you decide to burn it; "
"however, you will be able to use the compressed files elsewhere. Make sure "
"the original files are lossless (<emphasis>wav</emphasis> or <emphasis>FLAC</"
"emphasis>), otherwise the result will be unsatisfactory."
msgstr ""
"Ako trebate kompresovati audio, kreirajte novi audio CD projekt, dodajte "
"datoteke za konvertovanje i pritisnite dugme  <guilabel>Konvertuj numere</"
"guilabel>. Ovo neće uticati na sadržaj CD-a ako se odlučite da ih pržite; "
"međutim, moći čete koristiti kompresovane datoteke negdje drugo. Osigurajte "
"da originalne datoteke budu negubiljive  (<emphasis>wav</emphasis> ili "
"<emphasis>FLAC</emphasis>), inače će rezltat biti nezadovoljavajući."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The top line will be the title of the disk. In many cases this will be fine, "
"but if you would like to change this to something else, simply rename it "
"using the context menu."
msgstr ""
"Gornja linija će biti naslov diska. U mnogim slučajevima to će biti uredu, "
"ali ako biste željeli promijeniti ovo u nešto drugo, jednostavno ga "
"premenujte koristeći kontekstni meni."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid "Final Steps"
msgstr "Finalni koraci"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid "You are now ready to hit the <guilabel>Burn</guilabel> button."
msgstr "Sada ste spremni da pritisnete <guilabel>Prži</guilabel> dugme."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You will see on my screenshot that no disk was present. When you have "
"inserted the appropriate disk you will see a description of it on that line."
msgstr ""
"Vidjet ćete na mojoj slici ekrana da disk nije prisutan. Kada ste ubacili "
"odgovarajući disk vidjet ćete njegov opis na toj liniji."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are still one or two choices to be made. I would <emphasis>recommend</"
"emphasis> that you set <guilabel>Verify written data</guilabel>, then hit "
"the <guilabel>Save</guilabel> icon at the bottom of the screen, ensuring "
"that it becomes your personal default. For most modern drives it's safe to "
"leave mode and speed to <guilabel>Auto</guilabel>. If you may wish to burn "
"another copy of the disk at a later date, select <guilabel>Create image</"
"guilabel>, which will save having to set up the burn again. Set the number "
"of copies you want to burn, then, when you are satisfied, hit "
"<guilabel>Burn</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Preostaju još dva izbora. Zelio bih <emphasis>preporučiti</emphasis> da "
"postavite <guilabel>Potvrdi napisane podatke</guilabel>, pa pritisnite "
"<guilabel>Sačuvaj</guilabel> ikonu na dnu ekrana, osiguravajući da to "
"postaje vaš lični zadani izbor. Za moge moderne drajvove sigurno je ostaviti "
"mod i ubrzati do <guilabel>Auto</guilabel>. Ako biste željeli da pržite "
"drugu kopiju diska kasnije, odaberite <guilabel>Kreiraj sliku</guilabel>, "
"koja će spremiti postavku za ponovno prženje. Postavite broj kopija koje "
"želite pržiti, i kada ste zadovoljni, pritinite <guilabel>Prži</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid "Burning an Audio CD"
msgstr "Prženje Audio CD-a"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starting an Audio CD Project"
msgstr "Započinjanje Audio CD projekta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&k3b; supports a lot of audio formats and can convert them automatically for "
"you."
msgstr ""
"&k3b; podržava mnogo audio formata koje može automatski konvertovati za vas."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some distributions split this capability of &k3b; into a separate package, "
"&eg; on Debian and Ubuntu distributions you need to install the package "
"libk3b6-extracodecs, on openSUSE the name of the package is k3b-codecs. On "
"some distributions (&eg; Mandriva) you do not need to install any additional "
"packages."
msgstr ""
"Mnoge distibucije dijele ovu sposobnost &k3b;-a u odvojene pakete, &eg; na "
"Debian i Ubuntu distribucijama morate instalirati pakete libk3b6-"
"extracodecs, na openSUSE naziv paketa je  k3b-codecs. Na nekim "
"distribucijama (&eg; Mandriva) ne morate instalirati nikakve dodatne pakete."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selecting the files"
msgstr "Selektovanje datoteka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are two ways to select the audio files you want to burn onto an audio "
"cd:"
msgstr ""
"Postoje dva načina da selektujete audio datoteke koje želite pržiti na vaš "
"audio cd:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &k3b;"
msgstr "Korištenjem &k3b;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:223
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the bottom half of the &k3b; window click on <guilabel>New Audio CD "
"Project</guilabel> and select the files you want to burn."
msgstr ""
"Na donjoj polovici &k3b;  prozora kliknite na <guilabel>Novi Audio CD "
"Projekt</guilabel> i selektujte datoteke koje želite pržiti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alternatively navigate in the folders panel to the location of the audio "
"files. Double click on an audio file or drag and drop selected audio files "
"into the bottom part of &k3b;'s window automatically starts a <guilabel>New "
"Audio CD Project</guilabel> with these files."
msgstr ""
"Alternativno upravljajte folderskim panelom do lokacije audio datoteka. "
"Duplim klikom na audio datoteku ili povlačenjem i ispuštanjem selektovane "
"audio datoteke na donji dio prozora &k3b;-a automatski pokreće "
"<guilabel>Novi Audio CD Projekt</guilabel> sa ovim datotekama."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the file manager"
msgstr "Korištenje menadžera datoteka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Go to the folder containing your music files in &dolphin; or &konqueror;"
msgstr ""
"Idite na folder koji sadrži vaše muzičke datoteke u &dolphin; ili &konqueror;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the files to burn and select <menuchoice><guimenu>Actions</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Create Audio CD with &k3b;</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"from the context menu."
msgstr ""
"Odaberite datoteke za prženje i selektujte <menuchoice><guimenu>Radnje</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Kreiraj Audio CD sa &k3b;</guimenuitem></menuchoice> iz "
"kontekstnog menija."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edit the Title Information"
msgstr "Uredi Informaciju Naslova"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:242
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can give the tracks titles or import those from <acronym>CDDB</acronym> "
"(a online service for track names). To do so double click on the track "
"(lower half of the window)."
msgstr ""
"Možete dati numeri naslove ili ih uvesti iz <acronym>CDDB</acronym> (online "
"usluga za imena numera). Da biste to uradili dva puta klkliknite na numeru "
"( donja polovica ekrana)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid "Burn the CD"
msgstr "Prži CD"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Insert a blanc CD-R or CD-RW disc into your CD writer and click on "
"<guilabel>Burn</guilabel>. In the upcoming dialog check if you like the "
"presets and when done click on <guilabel>Burn</guilabel>. The CD will now be "
"burned for you."
msgstr ""
"Ubacite prazan CD-R ili CD-RW disk u vaš CD pisač i kliknite na "
"<guilabel>Prži</guilabel>. U dolazećem dijalogu označite ako biste željeli "
"presetovati i kada završite kliknite na   <guilabel>Prži</guilabel>. Cd če "
"sada biti pržen za vas."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid "Credits and License"
msgstr "Zasluge i Licenca"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:255
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Documentation Copyright see the UserBase <ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde."
#| "org/index.php?title=K3b&amp;action=history\">K3b page history</ulink>"
msgid ""
"Documentation Copyright see the UserBase <ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde."
"org/index.php?title=K3b&amp;action=history\">K3b page history</ulink>"
